        "rich_text_PA9wLd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Halo rings have been around for decades, but they continue to evolve with new styles.</p><p>Some halo rings have a vintage-inspired look, with delicate details and intricate metalwork. Others are designed with clean lines and modern shapes.</p><p>The Quadra Lattice Halo Diamond Ring is an example of how modern halo designs can include geometric patterns and bold structure.</p><p>On the other hand, the Long Cushion Cut Halo Diamond Ring reflects a more classic style that feels timeless.</p><p>Because halo settings are so adaptable, they can suit both traditional and contemporary tastes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xH7CqU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Halo Rings Add Brilliance Without Making the Ring Feel Too Heavy",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Halo Rings Add Brilliance Without Making the Ring Feel Too Heavy</h2>",
            "custom_id": "ring-feel",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_7YX8dw": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Solitaire_Rings_Are_Becoming_a_Popular_Choice_for_Men_Too.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UYNgNL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Even though halo rings include multiple diamonds, they often remain comfortable and balanced.</p><p>The smaller diamonds used in the halo are carefully placed to add sparkle without adding excessive weight to the ring. This makes halo rings suitable for everyday wear as well as special occasions.</p><p>Many people appreciate that a halo ring can look luxurious while still feeling light and wearable.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Many Buyers Choose Halo Rings for Engagements",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Many Buyers Choose Halo Rings for Engagements</h2><p>Halo rings have become a popular engagement ring style because they combine elegance with visual impact.</p><p>They offer several advantages:<br/><br/>1.] Extra sparkle around the center diamond<br/>2.] The illusion of a larger stone<br/>3.] Unique design options<br/>4.] A balanced, eye-catching appearance<br/><br/>Designs like the Elliptical Halo Diamond Ring or Canary Halo Diamond Ring show how halo settings can add personality while still feeling refined.</p><p>For couples choosing an engagement ring, this style often feels both special and expressive.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-many",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dUcxpz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lucira Approach to Halo Ring Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lucira Approach to Halo Ring Design</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, halo rings are crafted to highlight the beauty of the center diamond while maintaining comfort and durability.</p><p>Each ring is designed with IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, ensuring responsible sourcing while delivering exceptional brilliance.</p><p>From delicate vintage-inspired halos to bold modern shapes, Lucira halo rings are created to celebrate individuality while maintaining timeless elegance.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the-lucira",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
